ornamental tree and in multi-row windbreaks.  
Livestock: Grazing understory species can be helpful 
in reducing weed competition, however if young 
seedlings are grazed tree defects could occur 
resulting in low quality timber. 
Timber: Hackberry has limited value in the 
manufacture of paneling and furniture. 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
