large-flowered sensitive-pea, dwarf cassia, partridge 
pea senna, locust weed, golden cassia 
' WHERE symbol='chfa2';
ALTER TABLE usda_plants ADD fs_Uses TEXT;
UPDATE usda_plants SET fs_Uses='Wildlife: This plant provides food for birds. The seed 
is one of the major food items of northern bobwhite 
and quail because it remains in sound condition 
throughout the winter and early spring.   
Erosion control: The plant can be used along road 
banks and stream banks to control erosion. 
 
 
 
' WHERE symbol='chfa2';
