low as 3.8, (2) aluminum concentration which limits 
growth of other species, and (3) light textured soil 
which is droughty and infertile.  These tolerances 
allow deertongue to excel when revegetating acid 
coal and other surface mine spoils, and sandy infertile 
disturbed areas. 
