range of soil and climatic conditions.  It is adapted 
from the low elevation of the mountains to the open 
plains.  It has been widely tested and evaluated in 
Kansas, Oklahoma, northern Texas, New Mexico, 
Colorado, and portions of Nebraska. 
 
For a current distribution map, please consult the 
Plant Profile page for this species on the PLANTS 
Website. 
 
