seed processing.   There are approximately 1,300,000 
seeds/lb (+/- 30%).  A sowing rate of 1 lb per/ac of 
pure live seed will result in about 30 live seeds per 
square foot.  The potential high cost of seed may 
limit its use to mixtures with other native grasses.  
