reportedly not necessary.  The seed may be drilled on 
32-40 inch rows at 4.7 pounds per acre or broadcast 
at 5.2 pounds per acre.  The target rate is 45 PLS/ft 
when drilled and 15 PLS/ft2 when broadcasted.  ' WHERE symbol='hehes';
