Most crimson clover types used in the past were 
common types.  However, more recent introductions 
featured reseeding types such as ‘Dixie’, ‘Tibbee’, 
and ‘AU Robin’.  ‘AU Sunrise’ and ‘AU Sunup’ are 
reseeding cultivars from the Jimmy Carter Plant 
Materials Center in Americus, Georgia and Auburn 
University in Auburn, Alabama. The ‘AU Sunrise’ 
and ‘AU Sunup’ releases are well-adapted to 
Alabama and Georgia, and can grow into Florida and 
Mississippi. 
