Landscaping: It is an attractive flowering landscape 
plant for use in odd areas or in group plantings 
around homes and farm ponds.  The fruit is a bright 
red which increases its ornamental value.  Combined, 
its characteristics make it useful as a dual purpose 
food plant and ornamental. 
 
' WHERE symbol='viopa2';
