UPDATE usda_plants SET fs_='Uses 
Golden Alexanders has its greatest potential as a 
component of conservation mixes and wildflower 
gardens.  In wet, sunny meadows and open 
woodlands it will naturalize.  The flowers are 
attractive to many kinds of butterflies and many other 
insects.  It is an excellent source of accessible pollen 
and nectar to many beneficial insects with short 
mouthparts.  
' WHERE symbol='ziau';
